body:
I receive following error for below code.

```
$ iverilog -g2012 test.v
$ vvp a.out
DIRECT ASSIGNED STRING is WORKING
internal error: 18vvp_fun_anyedge_sa: recv_string(IDLE) not implemented
vvp: vvp_net.cc:3339: virtual void vvp_net_fun_t::recv_string(vvp_net_ptr_t, const string&, vvp_context_t): Assertion `0' failed.
Aborted
```

```systemverilog

module tb();

typedef enum logic [1:0] {  IDLE = 0, RESET = 1, START = 2, WAITFOR = 3} stateType;
stateType state;

string workingString = "WORKING";
initial begin
$display("DIRECT ASSIGNED STRING is ", workingString);
#10;
state = IDLE;
end

string state_txt;
always @* begin
    case(state)
        IDLE    : state_txt = "IDLE";
        RESET   : state_txt = "RST";
        START   : state_txt = "STRT";
        WAITFOR : state_txt = "WAIT";
    endcase
    $display("Controller's new state is %s",state_txt);
end

endmodule


```

